’Ů@2ca05c5bc230cace4cb83c753a3dd2332acd1996db0a319e5fd49f1bc8527973ÚźTitle: title: unlet
Path: Examples
Content:
Delete a variable from memory.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> let x = 42; unlet $x


```
Delete multiple variables from memory.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> let x = 1; let y = 2; unlet $x $y


```
Attempting to delete a built-in variable fails.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> unlet $nu


```
Attempting to delete a non-variable fails.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> unlet 42


```
